title: Nissan FAST MULTI - CA/JP/EL/ER/GL/GR/US/CA INF/EL INF/ER INF/US
description:
This is a complication of the latest nissan fast that can found on the web. For personal use 

only. All copyrights go to NISSAN


Installation instructions:

1)Mount the iso with daemon tools or decompress it with Winrar 
2)Go to (Mounting Drive/decompress directory)FASTPRGWIN2000SETUP and launch setup.exe to 

install the base program of nissan fast
3)Go to your installed directory and run Nfset.exe Go to cd-rom setup and select drive1 and 

set it to the "MAINDVD" directory in the iso you mounted/decompressed. Do the same with 

drive-2 and set it to "INFDVD". Press ok
4)Run Nissan menu for the start menu or Nfmenu.exe in your install directory
5)Enjoy and share/seed!


Further usage instructions in README/Manual (How to choose destinations).pdf included in the iso

Versions up to Month/Year:
CA 09/11
JP 04/09
EL 09/11
ER 07/11
GL 09/11
GR 07/11
US 09/11
CA INF 01/10
EL INF 05/11
ER INF 05/11
US INF 05/11

Only Australian/New Zealand FAST is missing.

Released by TnF
